    <h2>{`What are typical practices to avoid getting Liquidated?`}</h2>
    <p>{`Remaining aware of a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "vault.md"
      }}>{`Vault’s`}</a>{` condition is the Vault owner’s own responsibility. Ensuring that assets remain safe from Liquidation is entirely in the hands of each Vault owner. Below are some common practices to monitor the health of a Vault:`}</p>
